    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 48-49.</p><p>Rokkaku’s Sixteen Strikes</p><p>Strike, Zulfiqar</p><p>Classes: Fighter Channeling Time: 1 action Range: Weapon range or reach Duration: Instantaneous LP Cost: 2 LP</p><p>You infuse your weapon with a phantom echo of your own fighting spirit, and in a single devastating moment, every strike you could possibly deliver is realized at once.</p><p>As an action, you perform up to 16 special weapon attacks against targets within range. On a hit, each strike deals 20 Lethal damage.</p><p>These attacks do not benefit from Mythical Technique Infusions. On a critical hit, the damage for an attack is not doubled, but rather increases to 25. If the creature is bloodied and Lethal damage takes effect, the damage is not tripled; each critical strike deals 30 damage instead. These attacks do not benefit from any other bonus to their damage.</p><p>You can divide these attacks freely among any number of targets within range.</p><p>If you perform this technique with a ranged weapon, the maximum number of attacks is reduced to 12.</p></div>",
      "chat": ""
    },
